&lt;p&gt;Very clear question. I couldn&apos;t help but post the answer after a few hours of digging. We Could of solved this with tables, table-cell, absolute positions, transforms but we just had to do it with flexbox :)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-html s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-xml&quot;&gt;.parent {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: flex-end;
}

.center {
  margin: auto;
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

